modName: Farm Animals and Co. Extended Version
summary: This mod adds very many animals* in many places through Skyrim (farms especially, windmills, lakes**, towns, villages ...) . DLC Dragonborn needed
descriptionHtml:
[b][i]This mod adds very many animals* in many places through Skyrim (farms especially, windmills, lakes**, towns, villages ...) [/i][/b](DLC Dragonborn needed)


[color=#ff0000][b]WARNING[/b][/color]: If you have my mod [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/91142/?] Farm Animals and Co. [/url] You must delete it



*104 different animals (Boars, Chickens, Swan, Roosters, Chicks, Ducks, Ducklings, Geese, Cows, Goats, Sheeps, Ram, Pigs, Piglets, Young Wild Boar, Rabbits, Pigeons, Seagulls, Pheasants, Flamingos, Great Auks, Canada Geese, GuineaFowls, Vulturine GuineaFowls, Bar-headed Geese, Greater Roadrunners and Peacocks)

**Lake LLinalta (near Riverwood) - Lake Geir (near Ivarstead) - Lake Honrich (near Riften)


Will you be able to find them all ? … HEAR THEM !

New sounds (boar, flamingos, peacocks, swan, chickens, rabbits, pheasants, ram, cows, sheeps, goats, pigs, goose, pigeon, chick, duckling, ducks, roosters, seagull, great auk, canada goose, guineafowl, vulturine guineafowl, bar-headed goose, greater roadrunner)


For the « [b][color=#00ff00] Pack Goat [/color][/b] » you have [b]5 companions[/b] with the Dialog Box: Follow - Wait - Favor - Trade - Dismiss (in Half Moon Mill, Karthwasten, Chillfurrow Farm, Salvius Farm and near the Whiterun Stables) + 3 « wild » !



You can also place many of these animals in the place you want thanks to my mod: [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89775] Repopulate Skyrim with Farm Animals and Birds [/url]


[img]https://i.imgur.com/ZEJY9Oa.gif[/img]


You can only have one Follower at a time: if you want a different one (in my other mods), you need to dismiss the first one before you recruit them.

If telling the follower to return at home (With message: “Your companion heads home”) doesn't dismiss him, or if you have lost the active Follower, you can try this:

Type “²” or "`" or "~" key to get into console, and type:

set playeranimalcount to 0

With [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15524/?] Amazing Follower Tweaks [/url], or other mod with followers, if problem to dismiss the followers, you can uncheck this mod (AFT or other) in the Data Files when you launch the game

If problem with the Dialog Box of the followers/ companions (Wait - Follow - Trade - Favor - Dismiss) you can also enter / exit a house or make a fast travel

[img]https://i.imgur.com/B4GJ2hH.gif[/img]



[color=#ff0000][b] LOCATIONS of the RARE BIRDS[/b][/color]


Guineafowls (9) with real sounds : Pelagia Farm, Sarethi Farm and Whitewatch Tower

Canada Geese (37) with real sounds : on the South of Solitude Sawmill near the river, at the north of Heartwood Mill near the lake, and between Ivarstead and Nilheim near the lake

Vulturine guineafowls (7) with real sounds : Pelagia Farm and Half-Moon Mill

Greater roadrunner (30) with real sounds : on the road at the West of the western watchtower (near Whiterun) and the North of Battle-Born Farm

Bar-headed Goose (27) with real sounds : North Fort Greymoor and Between Bleakwind Basin and Halted Stream Camp, near the water

Peacocks (5) with real sounds : Falkreath + Chillfurrow Farm (near Whiterun)

Flamingos (10) with real sounds: Lake Honrich (near Riften)

Great Auks (20): Hela’s Foly, Pilgrim's Trench, Wreek of the Icerunner and near the Katariah

Palawan Peacock Pheasants (2) with real sounds: Honningbrew Meadery

White Eared Pheasants (2) with real sounds: near Riverwood

Green Pheasants (2) with real sounds: Falkreath

Silver Pheasants (2) with real sounds: Pelagia Farm

Mandarin Ducks (4) with real sounds: Honningbrew Meadery and Sarethi Farm

Black Mallard Ducks (3) : Chillfurrow Farm

Cinnamon Teal Ducks (4) with real sounds: near Riverwood

Labrador Ducks (12): Brandy Mug Farm, Nightgate Inn and Raven Rock (Solstheim)

Eurasian Wigeon Duck (4) with real sounds: Falkreath

Australian Shelducks (7) with real sounds / Shelducks Ducklings (5) : Falkreath

Farm Ducks (3) : Near Whiterun

Green Winged Teal Ducks (4) with real sounds : Near Whiterun

Philippine Duck (6) with real sounds : Near Whiterun and on isles on the South of Solitude Sawmill

Wood Ducks (4) with real sounds: Near Whiterun

Maccoas Ducks (4) with real sounds: Left Hand Mine

Black Ducks (5) : Kynesgrove

New Zealand Blue Ducks (4) with real sounds : Old Hroldan

Emerald Ducks (4) : Dark Brotherhood Sanctuary

Blue Ducks (6) : Darkwater Crossing

[img]https://i.imgur.com/IKo7dMX.gif[/img]

[color=#ff0000][b]CREDITS [/b][/color]


The textures of Goats , Cows and Chickens are from Bellyache; Mod [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/3621] Bellyaches Animal and Creature Pack [/url]("Asset use permission": "You are allowed to use the assets in this file without permission as long as you credit me").

Jc1 for the model of the Goose

dogtown1 to convert the model of the Goose in skyrim, and for the model of the Pig

The meshes and textures of the Sheeps are from stormshallow in his mod [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/33273] Sheep Modders Resource [/url]

Umar Muzammil [url=http://www.youtube.com/umar6419]UMAR6419 [/url] for the model of the sheep in this site [url=http://thefree3dmodels.com/stuff/0-0-2014-0-17] The free 3D Models [/url] ("You are free to use these models in generating games, animations, multimedia, printed graphics, web graphics and others" and "you are free to distribute and modify the file as long as you attribute it's author(s)")

cansu for the new texture of the Sheep in his mod [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/37569]stormshallows sheep mod retextured [/url]

testiger2 for the Mesh of the “Pack mule” for the goat in his mod [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68149/?] TesTiger's Mesh Resources [/url]

KANRAx2 with his Mod: [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/38138/?]yurufuwa rabbit [/url] ("Modders resources and tutorials") for the meshes and the textures of the rabbits, and the mod [url=http://skyrimshot.blog.fc2.com/blog-entry-49.html]Kanra Follower [/url]+ [url=https://rim-rim-fox.tumblr.com/post/77800883762/kanrafollower-addon-2] kanrafollower_addon [/url]; [url=http://sala-mitzha.tumblr.com/] Blog of Kanra/Sala mitzha [/url]

LorSakyamuni for the models of a few animals in his mod [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76524/?] The Witcher 3 Monsters and Animals Resource Pack [/url] (“You are allowed to use the assets in this file without permission as long as you credit me”,“Pack containing a lot of monsters and animals included in the game The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt. All the original assets belong to [url=https://en.cdprojektred.com/] CD PROJEKT RED [/url] and are distributed with their permission. Feel free to use them, just remember to credit me.”). Some animals are rigged by SpikeDragonLord and jboyd4 in the mod [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/76203/?]Beasts of Tamriel[/url]

Mihail Romanov for the birds (Chick, Bantam Chickens, Ducklings, Ducks, Roosters, Pheasants) in [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89772/] Pheasants Ducks and Chickens- Elements of Skyrim pt.13 (mihail immersive add-ons- animal- birds) [/url], for the Pigeon in [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89548] Pigeons- Elements of Skyrim pt.12 (mihail immersive add-ons- birds)[/url], for the Great Auk in [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/88927] Chub Loons - Mihail Monsters and Animals (mihail immersive add-ons- ESO - birds) [/url], for the Seagull in [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/89528/] Seagulls -Elements of Skyrim pt.10 (mihail immersive add-ons- birds) [/url], for the Boars in [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/90127] Boars and Daggerbacks- Mihail Monsters and Animals (mihail immersive add-ons- oblivion- eso) [/url], for the Flamingos in [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/88066/] Flamingos - Elements of Skyrim pt. 6 (mihail immersive add-ons - birds) [/url], for the Canada Geese, the GuineaFowls, the Vulturine, the Bar-headed Goose, the Roadrunner in [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/91998/] Geese and Hammerfell Fowls- Elements of Skyrim pt.15 (mihail immersive add-ons- birds) [/url], and for the Peacocks in [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/81868/?] Peacocks- Mihail Monsters and Animals (mihail immersive add-ons- animals- birds) [/url] ("Feel free to use my mod in your projects, no need to ask me for permission first")

Kaizit and Tamira in [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/54677] Ducks and Swans Resource [/url]
